==Tailoring==
Hazelnut is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the [[Tailoring|Brown Overalls]].  [[File:Shirt266.png|24px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
*The Hazelnut may be randomly requested in [[Fall]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|270}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

